### Actor-Actor Similarity

  • Co-mention rate is normalized by individual mention rates

    • \[ \frac{ab}{ \sqrt{ |a||b| }} \sim \frac{ \textrm{# of co-mentions}}{ \sqrt{ \textrm{# of } a\textrm{'s mentions} \times \textrm{# of } b\textrm{'s mentions} } } \\[10pt]\]
      • Known as cosine similarity
